---
title: One-Pan Tuscan Chicken Sausage & White Beans with Tomatoes, Zucchini, Ricotta & Parmesan Croutons
description: Love the flavors of pizza? Of course, you do, you’re only human! Our chefs have channeled our favorite late-night bite into a one-pan dinner, packed with veggies and protein. Zucchini and cannellini beans simmer with tomatoes for the saucy component, which gets dolloped with creamy, mild ricotta cheese. Next? Hello, big, crunchy croutons! And a final flourish of Parm gets all melty when popped into the oven. Where has this skillet bean all our lives??
